"
I am announced when an MGCard is flipped (either face-up or face-down).

I am used by MGCard to notify observers (such as UI elements) that the card's flip state has changed, so they can update their visual representation.

See also: MGCard>>flip, MGCard>>notifyFlipped
"
Class {
	#name : 'MGCardFlippedAnnouncement',
	#superclass : 'Announcement',
	#category : 'Bloc-Memory',
	#package : 'Bloc-Memory'
}
